{"tid":1513281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"杭州市區道路突然塌陷　黃色瓦斯煙霧籠罩彌漫","createTime":"2019-08-28T09:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T16:07:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":150,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"f583f04f5336271449bc08d746bc8ac83921d268","tid":1513281,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:09:39.000Z","msg":"杭州市區道路突然塌陷　黃色瓦斯煙霧籠罩彌漫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2019/08/1117593.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgotv.ctitv.com.tw%2F2019%2F08%2F1117593.htm&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5Ex5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=29ffafba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gotv.ctitv.com.tw/2019/08/1117593.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n浙江杭州的建國北路、濱河公寓正對面的馬路，今天中午12點多突然塌陷，疑似拉斷天然氣管線，現場湧出大量黃色煙霧，快速順風籠罩路面及隣近建築，遮天蔽日，現場民眾都聞到濃濃的瓦斯味。<br />\n<br />\n第一時間趕到現場的民警立刻勸導行人熄滅香菸、要求周邊商家、住戶關閉煤氣、電源，離開家門，疏散到煙霧以外的戶外空地。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生後，一度有網友指出一旁的公車站也隨之塌陷，但民警表示，公車站並沒有塌陷，只是車站旁邊有塌陷，車站只是傾斜，但塌陷面積持續擴大，疑似有路過的電瓶車掉進去，暫時沒有傳出人員傷亡消息。杭州天然氣公司工作人員獲報趕到現場，正在處理。"},{"pid":"5ff7e836c789bbf595f83a5fa8b7c0fa59396474","tid":1513281,"uid":64278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"相?"},{"pid":"7fa790b07478c29ec844eba697f4f5e395f31136","tid":1513281,"uid":132611,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5ff7e836c789bbf595f83a5fa8b7c0fa59396474","tid":1513281,"uid":64278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"相?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"入link咪有"},{"pid":"42a27bc0249e59412448bc7b8a2c3537ae3c0376","tid":1513281,"uid":156781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:15:20.000Z","msg":"留名等睇出圖."},{"pid":"70461e396015fc0be7d471a48d2f0f5be930c039","tid":1513281,"uid":76310,"like":136,"dislike":0,"score":136,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s3-ap-northeast-1.amazonaws.com/pic.ctitv.com/wpimg/2019/08/28153119/%E6%9D%AD%E5%B7